    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款第三人称无双动作Roguelike游戏，你将扮演一位光明骑士抵御暗影帝国的入侵。利用圣光的力量，你可以将被影子感染的敌人变成友军。尝试坚持到黎明吧！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>作者声明</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《曙光之刃》是我们参加了一个游戏开发活动，花费14天制作出来的Demo，我们希望将其在Steam上进行展示以获得更多反馈意见(这对于我们将来的游戏开发很有用)。欢迎各位游玩~</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>砍杀与生存</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑暗中敌人源源不断的来袭，尽情砍杀他们，你有多个技能可以让你在人群中无双</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330530/extras/a4a5bbaa38b192101e9bdbbad7b33e39.poster.avif?t=1735992661\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330530/extras/a4a5bbaa38b192101e9bdbbad7b33e39.webm?t=1735992661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330530/extras/a4a5bbaa38b192101e9bdbbad7b33e39.mp4?t=1735992661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>选择升级路线</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败一定数量敌人后，可以获得一次升级的机会，你可以提升属性 or 获得新的特性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330530/extras/9a655b2902af2c395b60cf8c3f081408.avif?t=1735992661\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330530/extras_big/9a655b2902af2c395b60cf8c3f081408.avif?t=1735992661 width=800 height=470 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>转变敌人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用您的终极技能（T），可以一定概率将敌人转化为友军。利用这一点在怪海中存活吧！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>操作说明</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WSAD移动，左键攻击，QERT释放技能。</p>",
